k style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-link-color\">International students are permitted to work full-time during semester breaks and part-time while they are enrolled in classes in Norway. This may help you obtain real-world experience.</mark></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-link-color\">In conclusion, choosing to pursue higher education in Norway provides a special fusion of top-notch academics, breathtaking scenery, cultural experiences, and a high standard of living.</mark></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Norway',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'78-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2024-11-12 05:28:04',	'2024-11-12 05:28:04',	'',	78,	'http://localhost/brightdaysoverseastvm/?p=1469',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
